'''Calimehtar''' ([[Quenya|Q]] "Light-warrior", pron. {{IPA|[ˌkaliˈmeçtar]}} or in [[Gondor]] {{IPA|[ˌkaliˈmeʃtar]}}) can refer to two [[Gondorians]]: 
* [[Calimehtar (son of Calmacil)|Calimehtar]] (born after {{TA|1126}}), younger brother of [[Kings of Gondor|King]] [[Rómendacil II]], and grandfather of [[Castamir|Castamir the Usurper]].
* [[Calimehtar (King of Gondor)|Calimehtar]] ({{TA|1736}} - {{TA|1936|n}}), thirtieth [[Kings of Gondor|King]] of [[Gondor]] who defeated the [[Wainriders]].
